00:01:31.470 --> 00:01:32.470
What's He Jie's

00:01:32.589 --> 00:01:34.270
connection to Jiang Honghai?

00:01:36.589 --> 00:01:38.270
I've told you everything I know.

00:01:38.270 --> 00:01:39.029
Go arrest him.

00:01:39.029 --> 00:01:40.669
Why do you keep questioning me?

00:01:45.750 --> 00:01:47.070
Then let's start with this.

00:01:51.149 --> 00:01:51.990
Who is this?

00:01:57.789 --> 00:01:59.309
It's too blurry. I can't see clearly.

00:01:59.869 --> 00:02:00.669
What?

00:02:01.070 --> 00:02:02.584
You forgot who you ate with that day?

00:02:04.669 --> 00:02:05.470
Jiang Han.

00:02:06.350 --> 00:02:07.869
Does he know Jiang Honghai too?

00:02:08.549 --> 00:02:09.709
We're from the same village.

00:02:09.709 --> 00:02:10.350
He's a mason.

00:02:10.350 --> 00:02:11.870
He referred all the masons.

00:02:12.070 --> 00:02:13.470
Why didn't you mention it earlier?

00:02:13.549 --> 00:02:15.549
I didn't know he was involved in this.

00:02:15.750 --> 00:02:16.709
Check this guy out.

00:02:26.669 --> 00:02:27.829
What's Jiang Honghai's

00:02:27.870 --> 00:02:29.509
connection to the rape case

00:02:29.509 --> 00:02:30.590
22 years ago?

00:02:31.310 --> 00:02:32.989
That day, a lot of police
came to my place.

00:02:35.549 --> 00:02:36.709
All there to arrest me.

00:02:37.269 --> 00:02:38.669
They said I got a young girl

00:02:38.669 --> 00:02:39.829
pregnant.

00:02:40.669 --> 00:02:41.829
But I never did it.

00:02:41.829 --> 00:02:43.470
I didn't even know her.

00:02:45.269 --> 00:02:47.870
But that kid described everything
about me clearly.

00:02:50.750 --> 00:02:52.150
She even had my underwear.

00:02:54.310 --> 00:02:55.509
I only found out later

00:02:58.269 --> 00:02:59.989
that Honghai was behind that.

00:03:02.310 --> 00:03:03.709
It was all planned.

00:03:03.989 --> 00:03:05.269
You're saying

00:03:05.269 --> 00:03:07.870
Jiang Honghai and He Jie

00:03:09.350 --> 00:03:12.070
colluded to frame you?

00:03:12.350 --> 00:03:13.310
Not just them.

00:03:17.109 --> 00:03:18.310
Honghai's dad too.

00:03:19.949 --> 00:03:20.870
And my own dad.

00:03:21.389 --> 00:03:23.549
Then why would the victim
falsely accuse you?

00:03:24.949 --> 00:03:26.590
Honghai was 25 that year.

00:03:28.070 --> 00:03:29.030
He got her pregnant

00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:30.630
and secretly took her
to get an abortion.

00:03:30.630 --> 00:03:32.034
He Jie's parents called the police.

00:03:34.389 --> 00:03:36.070
Honghai couldn't go to jail.

00:03:38.789 --> 00:03:39.789
So he and He Jie

00:03:41.549 --> 00:03:43.549
threw the blame on me

00:03:44.590 --> 00:03:46.350
while his dad came to see my dad.

00:03:49.989 --> 00:03:51.430
His dad was a village official.

00:03:51.989 --> 00:03:53.630
He turned everyone against me.

00:03:55.789 --> 00:03:57.509
Even the police were fooled.

00:03:57.750 --> 00:03:59.229
My family couldn't fight them.

00:03:59.509 --> 00:04:01.669
Later, he gave us 20,000 yuan

00:04:02.509 --> 00:04:03.590
and an acre of land.

00:04:17.269 --> 00:04:18.630
(My dad told me...)

00:04:20.990 --> 00:04:21.790
"Son,

00:04:24.190 --> 00:04:24.990
just admit it."

00:04:41.550 --> 00:04:42.630
She's all settled in.

00:04:42.630 --> 00:04:43.430
Don't worry.

00:04:47.070 --> 00:04:48.550
We almost caught him.

00:04:49.870 --> 00:04:51.750
I should've anticipated his next move.

00:04:52.589 --> 00:04:54.149
His target has been Chen Xiaomeng.

00:04:56.269 --> 00:04:57.870
Calm down.

00:04:57.870 --> 00:04:59.469
How can I calm down?

00:04:59.990 --> 00:05:01.589
He almost succeeded.

00:05:02.230 --> 00:05:04.070
He's a murderer, a rapist.

00:05:04.550 --> 00:05:05.949
As I've already said,

00:05:05.949 --> 00:05:07.870
