to protect Chen Xiaomeng.

00:05:08.630 --> 00:05:09.389
Let's head back.

00:05:09.389 --> 00:05:11.070
Captain Leng might have new leads.

00:05:12.149 --> 00:05:13.230
Let's go. I'll drive.

00:05:19.509 --> 00:05:20.310
Let's go.

00:05:41.949 --> 00:05:42.589
Captain Leng.

00:05:44.670 --> 00:05:45.349
We got something.

00:05:46.029 --> 00:05:48.070
Jiang Han, 40 years old,
no prior record.

00:05:48.230 --> 00:05:49.589
He also grew up in the village.

00:05:49.589 --> 00:05:51.550
He's around the same age
as Jiang Lianhong.

00:05:51.550 --> 00:05:53.269
