00:05:53.349 --> 00:05:55.190
and helps young villagers find work.

00:05:55.790 --> 00:05:57.349
Bring Jiang Han in immediately.

00:05:57.949 --> 00:05:59.349
See if we can get

00:05:59.349 --> 00:06:00.589
new leads from him.

00:06:00.829 --> 00:06:02.750
Focus on finding Jiang Honghai.

00:06:02.949 --> 00:06:04.070
Yes, sir. I'm on it.

00:06:05.131 --> 00:06:07.864
(Ye Qian: Chen Xiaomeng is safe.)

00:06:12.110 --> 00:06:12.990
Should be here.

00:06:16.070 --> 00:06:16.750
Jiang Han?

00:06:22.430 --> 00:06:23.349
City Police Department.

00:06:24.269 --> 00:06:25.389
A few questions.

00:06:26.509 --> 00:06:28.349
I'm just a trainer.

00:06:28.709 --> 00:06:30.310
Conditions in our village aren't good.

00:06:30.509 --> 00:06:32.870
Many young guys rely on this skill

00:06:32.870 --> 00:06:33.949
to make a living.

00:06:34.328 --> 00:06:35.990
(Yunxi Police)
Did you refer Jiang Lianhong too?

00:06:36.829 --> 00:06:37.790
Jiang Lianhong?

00:06:40.190 --> 00:06:42.230
We do manual labor,

00:06:42.750 --> 00:06:44.230
but jobs aren't easy to find now.

00:06:45.029 --> 00:06:47.509
But he got lucky.

00:06:47.509 --> 00:06:48.870
Met some good people.

00:06:49.190 --> 00:06:51.790
Someone pulled strings
to pay his training fees.

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:52.709
Later on,

00:06:52.709 --> 00:06:54.709
they even gave him jobs
on construction sites.

00:06:55.829 --> 00:06:56.949
Who was that person?

00:06:57.509 --> 00:06:58.310
Jiang Honghai.

00:06:58.870 --> 00:07:00.990
His family used to be
in the renovation business.

00:07:01.630 --> 00:07:02.750
They're pretty well-off.

00:07:02.750 --> 00:07:04.509
His dad used to be a village official.

00:07:04.790 --> 00:07:06.110
Most of the fishponds

00:07:06.110 --> 00:07:07.589
in our village belong to his family.

00:07:08.589 --> 00:07:09.149
Right.

00:07:09.430 --> 00:07:10.430
Honghai has this habit.

00:07:10.949 --> 00:07:12.990
He loves making soup
with live brood fish.

00:07:13.469 --> 00:07:14.349
Says it's nourishing.

00:07:14.750 --> 00:07:15.990
He has it every single day.

00:07:16.349 --> 00:07:18.550
So, he always keeps
a fish tank where he lives.

00:07:19.269 --> 00:07:20.509
Every few days,

00:07:20.990 --> 00:07:23.230
he has his family
deliver fresh brood fish to him.

00:07:24.070 --> 00:07:24.949
You may not know.

00:07:25.389 --> 00:07:26.709
Brood fish are really expensive.

00:07:27.310 --> 00:07:28.829
Luckily, his family has fishponds.

00:07:29.589 --> 00:07:31.550
Or who could've afforded that?

00:07:32.331 --> 00:07:32.990
(Yunxi Police)

00:07:32.990 --> 00:07:34.310
On May 25th,

00:07:34.430 --> 00:07:36.430
where were you
between 10 PM and midnight?

00:07:37.550 --> 00:07:38.750
May 25th?

00:07:39.149 --> 00:07:39.949
Let me think.

00:07:41.349 --> 00:07:43.430
That night,
I was drinking at a restaurant.

00:07:44.149 --> 00:07:45.750
Who were you drinking with?

00:07:46.190 --> 00:07:48.670
Jiang Lianhong and Jiang Honghai.

00:07:49.029 --> 00:07:50.790
But Jiang Honghai can't hold his liquor.

00:07:51.110 --> 00:07:53.190
He was clamoring to leave before 11 PM.

00:07:53.349 --> 00:07:55.149
I drank for a bit longer
and then left too.

00:07:55.149 --> 00:07:56.829
Didn't pay attention to the exact time.

00:07:57.790 --> 00:07:59.589
Did you see Jiang Honghai again
after that?

00:08:00.029 --> 00:08:00.750
No.

00:08:02.149 --> 00:08:03.670
Besides home and construction sites,

00:08:03.670 --> 00:08:04.550
does Jiang Honghai

00:08:04.550 --> 00:08:05.750
have any other places to stay?

00:08:07.670 --> 00:08:09.469
Jiang Honghai is a strange one.

00:08:09.670 --> 00:08:11.070
He's used to keeping to himself.

00:08:12.389 --> 00:08:15.269
But I have a storage warehouse.

00:08:15.949 --> 00:08:17.630
A year ago, he asked me for its key

00:08:17.630 --> 00:08:19.630
and wanted to keep
construction equipment there.

00:08:19.630 --> 00:08:21.430
He hasn't returned the key yet.

00:08:21.670 --> 00:08:23.389
Where is that warehouse?

00:08:23.949 --> 00:08:25.469
28, North Xinyuan Lane.

00:08:25.670 --> 00:08:27.389
In the abandoned place
by the noodle shop.

00:08:40.310 --> 00:08:41.109
We got something.

00:08:41.829 --> 00:08:43.829
Jiang Honghai also drank
with them that night.

00:08:43.829 --> 00:08:44.709
And he left first.

00:08:45.070 --> 00:08:45.629
Wang Tong,

00:08:46.030 --> 00:08:46.872
