00:09:19.709 --> 00:09:20.390
Wang Tong.

00:09:20.390 --> 00:09:21.510
- You take point.
- Okay.

00:09:21.510 --> 00:09:22.270
You provide backup.

00:09:22.550 --> 00:09:23.790
We secure the perimeter.

00:11:05.790 --> 00:11:06.390
Get down.

00:11:08.030 --> 00:11:08.709
Don't move.

00:11:31.310 --> 00:11:34.109
Jiang Lianhong wanted to cover for you

00:11:35.550 --> 00:11:36.629
and take the blame for you.

00:11:37.589 --> 00:11:38.430
Did you know that?

00:11:42.829 --> 00:11:43.390
He...

00:11:45.869 --> 00:11:46.869
he might have been

00:11:48.469 --> 00:11:49.469
doing it for his dad.

00:11:49.740 --> 00:11:55.352
(Dual usage of devices
is strictly prohibited)

00:11:56.829 --> 00:11:59.229
Why protect Jiang Honghai?

