00:12:14.190 --> 00:12:15.349
Once, when we were drunk,

00:12:16.550 --> 00:12:17.510
he told me,

00:12:18.829 --> 00:12:19.709
"Lianhong,

00:12:20.229 --> 00:12:22.150
if anything ever happens to you,

00:12:23.469 --> 00:12:25.229
I'll take care of your dad
until the end."

00:12:26.629 --> 00:12:27.469
Well,

00:12:29.589 --> 00:12:30.550
