00:12:32.949 --> 00:12:34.469
Whether I live or die doesn't matter.

00:12:36.070 --> 00:12:37.550
Back then, you seduced He Jie

00:12:38.949 --> 00:12:40.510
and got her pregnant at just 13.

00:12:41.070 --> 00:12:42.310
After her parents found out,

00:12:42.469 --> 00:12:44.070
you forced her to commit perjury

00:12:44.989 --> 00:12:47.510
and pinned all the blame
on Jiang Lianhong.

00:12:48.390 --> 00:12:50.270
Now you've committed these three crimes.

00:12:50.629 --> 00:12:52.390
You've destroyed five families.

00:12:57.419 --> 00:13:02.264
(Dual usage of devices
is strictly prohibited)

00:13:09.109 --> 00:13:10.270
Why target them?

00:13:20.749 --> 00:13:21.550
Jiang Honghai,

00:13:22.949 --> 00:13:24.270
you won't get away this time.

00:13:25.510 --> 00:13:26.949
No one can take the fall for you.

00:13:27.310 --> 00:13:28.869
You reap what you sow.

00:13:29.030 --> 00:13:30.270
The law will get you.

00:13:30.508 --> 00:13:31.896
(Jiang Honghai finally pleaded guilty
in the face of evidence.)

00:13:31.896 --> 00:13:33.176
(For the case of his false accusation
against Jiang Lianhong 22 years ago,)

00:13:33.176 --> 00:13:34.584
