00:14:11.229 --> 00:14:12.430
in the right direction.

00:14:13.190 --> 00:14:14.150
So the suffering before

00:14:14.829 --> 00:14:15.949
won't have been in vain.

00:14:18.390 --> 00:14:19.349
Understood, master.

00:14:19.430 --> 00:14:20.229
