00:15:38.949 --> 00:15:40.030
It wasn't your fault.

00:15:41.550 --> 00:15:43.150
He will face severe punishment.

00:15:46.589 --> 00:15:47.270
Thank you.

00:16:06.604 --> 00:16:07.174
